==English==

===Alternative spellings===
*[[voila]]

===Etymology===
French

===Interjection===
'''voilà''' (''often'' '''[[voila]]!''')

# "Lo! There it is"

===Usage notes===
In the English language, diacritics are usually dropped from borrowed words.  Some prescriptivists insist that the diacritic is not only correct, but that not having it is a spelling error (even though that diacritic doesn't exist in the English alphabet.)  Other prescribe that the near impossibility of entering the character on US keyboards dictate that [[voila]] is the only correct spelling in English.

